entity.name: Warning issued for Barbados as Tropical Storm Dorian approaches
entity.description: The National Hurricane Center issued a tropical storm warning for Barbados on Sunday as Tropical Storm Dorian approaches the island. A tropical storm watch is in effect for St. Lucia, St. Vincent and the Grenadines.

entity.name: Tropical Storm Dorian picks up strength as it nears landfall in Puerto Rico
entity.description: Forecasters say Tropical Storm Dorian could reach near-hurricane strength as it makes landfall in Puerto Rico on Wednesday.
